Testing #183545

I might be doing something wrong, my contribution:

```json
"contributes": {
  "commands": [
    {
      "command": "status-ts.helloWorld",
      "title": "Hello World"
    }
  ],
  "statusBarItems": {
    "id": "benj",
    "name": "Benj Status Items",
    "text": "$(remote) My Text",
    "alignment": "left",
    "command": "status-ts.helloWorld"
  }
}
```

I see no status entry that I can click on. I also tried with an existing command such as `vscode.open`. 

![Recording 2023-05-30 at 11 29 52](https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/assets/900690/9cf1eca7-0c06-4466-9216-4c618764f7ce)


Extension code is a hello world:

```ts
